          "[?0>failOld;ths:=t;hhs:=h;shs:=as;][d:=*;?0<=d;?d<=as;{t'=1,c'=1,h'=min(iMAX(),ai)-d&c<=TS()}]((0<=ai&ai<=iMAX()&as<=sMAX()&TS()>=c&c>=0&(0=0|0=1))&h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()&(0=1&hhs>=hMAX()&shs>=sMAX()&t-ths<=tMAX()->h>=hhs-sMAX()*(t-ths)&h>=hDEG()&as>=sDEG()))":
